Introduction

JL is a Filipino singer under ShowBT Entertainment, a Filipino-based company.

He first debuted in the Filipino boy group PLUUS on February 8, 2023, with the release of their first mini-album "+.Y.M." (also known as "PLUUS +.Y.M.;" read as Time).

He was a contestant in SBS' survival show Universe League, where he ranked 1st place overall, securing his spot as a member of the final group AHOF.
